    "body": "If you haven’t already, check out our [contributing guidelines](https://github.com/Expensify/ReactNativeChat/blob/main/contributingGuides/CONTRIBUTING.md) for onboarding and email contributors@expensify.com to request to join our Slack channel!\n___\n\n**Version Number:** 9.3.34\n**Reproducible in staging?:** Needs Reproduction (Unable to reproduce)\n**Reproducible in production?:** Needs Reproduction\n**If this was caught during regression testing, add the test name, ID and link from BrowserStack:**\n**Email or phone of affected tester (no customers):**\n**Logs:** https://stackoverflow.com/c/expensify/questions/4856\n**Expensify/Expensify Issue URL:**\n**Issue reported by:** @nicollyrodrigues-max \n**Slack conversation** (hyperlinked to channel name): #[Expensify Bugs](https://expensify.slack.com/archives/C049HHMV9SM/p1773251205200679)\n\n## Action Performed:\n\n1. User navigates to Reports.\n2. Clicks on Expenses.\n3. Selects a specific expense item.\n4. Attempts to open it to review or edit.\n\n## Expected Result:\nUser should be able to open, view, and edit all of their expense items without receiving an access error.\n## Actual Result:\nSome expenses open normally. However, certain expenses consistently return the error message and cannot be accessed or modified.\nIssue persists after trouble shooting steps. (Fully closed browser and cleared cache/cookies. and Clear cache and restart.)\n## Workaround:\nUnknown\n## Platforms:\nSelect the officially supported platforms where the issue was reproduced:\n- [ ] Android: App\n- [ ] Android: mWeb Chrome\n- [x] iOS: App\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Safari\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Chrome\n- [x] Windows: Edge\n- [ ] MacOS: Chrome / Safari\n\n## Screenshots/Videos\n\nThe screenshots for the issue are in Slack [thread](https://expensify.slack.com/archives/C049HHMV9SM/p1773251205200679)\n\n[View all open jobs on GitHub](https://github.com/Expensify/App/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3A%22Help+Wanted%22)\n\n\n<details><summary>Issue Owner</summary>Current Issue Owner: @linhvovan29546</details>\n<details><summary>Upwork Automation - Do Not Edit</summary>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Upwork Job URL: https://www.upwork.com/jobs/~022031884737048244849</li>\n        <li>Upwork Job ID: 2031884737048244849</li>\n        <li>Last Price Increase: 2026-03-12</li>\n    </ul>\n</details>",
